author: jholmes
msg: Fix test failures caused by the fix for WW-1618. It turns out that the doubleId was not being handled consistent with the way id is handled. I updated DoubleListUIBean.java to handle doubleId the same way as id. Basically doubleId will now be assigned the same value as doubleName if doubleId does not have a value.
